3) lexical scope
lexical scope ko static scope bhi kaha jata h
mtb isske accessesiblity of varibales code ke structure ke basis pr hoti h na ki kha likha gya iss mai depend kregi 

functions are scoped to where they are written in the source code not where they are called from 


lexical scoping with closures is a way of doing data hiding showing only relevent important things know as data abstraction 

flow of oops = abstraction,encapsulation,polymorphism,inheritance.




